App-cpan-reports

Installs cpan-reports script for downloading a distributions CPAN Testers
test reports.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc App::cpan-reports

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=App-cpan-reports

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/App-cpan-reports

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/App-cpan-reports

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/App-cpan-reports/

    Source Code
        git://github.com/ivanwills/App-cpan-reports.git

